We are new to the area. At noon yesterday, my husband and his friends were catching up at McDonalds. They accidentally dropped their wallets and didnt know it. The next morning when I got home, I realized that I would go back and ask the waiter immediately. I never expected that they would return it to my husband intact. I was so touched at the time! Thank you McDonalds for your trustworthy service attitude. Will always support in the future.
